### 4. Constitutional Guardrails Instead of Prompt Engineering

**Traditional:** "Please behave nicely" prompts and complex system messages
**Consulate:** Constitutional rules as code with economic incentives

```typescript
// In convex/constitution.ts - Rules are code, not prompts
export const AUTO_RULES = [
  {
    code: "SLA_MISS",
    description: "Service Level Agreement violation",
    category: "performance",
    enabled: true,
  }
];

// Real economic stakes, not just prompts
case "premium":
